Package: nflForecastR
Title: NFL Game Prediction and Analysis Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Eli", "Vatsaas", email = "eli.vatsaas@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for NFL game prediction and analysis. 
    Provides functions for processing NFL game data, creating prediction models,
    analyzing market efficiency, and visualizing results. This package is intended 
    for educational and research purposes only. The tools and analyses provided 
    should not be used as the sole basis for gambling or betting decisions. Users 
    assume all responsibility for any decisions made using this package, including 
    compliance with applicable laws and regulations regarding sports betting.
